AGI - A forty-six-year-old was arrested in the night in Soto de Ribera, a small town in the Asturias, while playing football on the street with his father's head, whose beheaded body was found in the house where the man lived with his parent, in the nearby village of Picòn. The possible motives of the murder are still unknown, explaining the Spanish media.
&nbsp;
Covered with blood and naked from the cintola up, the suspect, in evident state of alteration, hurled against the cars of the Civil Guard to arrest him after the alarm launched by the encapsulated passers in the macabre scene. Witnesses told 'El Magazineico' that they saw the man at the center of a roundabout while kicking the head of the elderly victim, scaling him against the passing vehicles, and branding the axe used for the parricidium, never stop laughing. On the arrival of the Civil Guard, the forty-six-year-old launched three times against one of the intervened means, before being blocked, arrested and admitted into a psychiatric ward. &nbsp;
